arStrings.szText: "You seem perturbed, did you need help with something?"
Yes! I need a bit of help from an outsider. I befriended a lacuni. Wem, I call him. I fed him a few times...I know what youâ€™re thinking but I...well, I think he's tribeless.
Usually lacuni stay away from settlements but some merchants caught him close to town. Poor cat...I think he was looking for me. Can you help me free him? They have him by Drowning Rock.
